6:["$","p",null,{"children":"After visiting the client at their business location and checking out their selection of buildings, I began some quick sketches. Oftentimes this is an easy way to capture some of the shapes that could be helpful in creating a logo. In this case, it was barn doors, transom windows, dormers, etc."}]
